snippet.title: Himno - Official Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Himno is a peaceful, 2D platformer game with an infinite number of beautiful procedurally generated maps. Take a breath, and relax.

Steam store: https://store.steampowered.com/app/931690/Himno/

Game by David Moralejo Sánchez
Twitter: https://twitter.com/BreakfastStudi1

Publisher: GrabTheGames
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GrabTheGames
